# Component Format Template - TNLL Explore

> Use this template as a **prompt/reference** for applying consistent compact design and emerald theme across all pages.

---

## üé® Color Palette (Emerald/Teal Theme)

```
Primary Gradient: from-emerald-500 to-teal-600
Secondary Gradient: from-teal-500 to-cyan-600
Text Gradient: from-emerald-600 to-teal-600 (for bg-clip-text)

Background Blurs:
- from-emerald-100/20 to-teal-100/10 (decorative orbs)
- from-cyan-100/20 to-blue-100/10 (accent orbs)

Badge/Tag: bg-emerald-50 border-emerald-100 text-emerald-700
Hover States: hover:text-emerald-600, hover:bg-emerald-50
Active States: text-emerald-600 bg-emerald-50/80
```

