## üé¨ GSAP Animation Patterns

### Entrance Animation
```javascript
gsap.fromTo('.element', 
    { opacity: 0, y: 30 }, 
    { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 0.6, stagger: 0.06, ease: 'power3.out',
      scrollTrigger: { trigger: '.element', start: 'top 80%', toggleActions: 'play none none reverse' }
    }
);
```

### Floating Background Decoration
```javascript
gsap.to('.deco', { 
    y: 'random(-10, 10)', 
    x: 'random(-6, 6)', 
    scale: 'random(0.94, 1.06)', 
    duration: 'random(6, 9)', 
    repeat: -1, yoyo: true, ease: 'sine.inOut', stagger: 1 
});
```

